+groups:
+  - name: ml_phase3_1_vertex_local_handoff_v1
+    rules:
+      - alert: MLVertexLocalHandoffStale
+        expr: time() - ml_vertex_local_handoff_last_run_ts_seconds > 1800
+        for: 10m
+        labels: { severity: warning }
+        annotations:
+          summary: "vertex local fallback handoff controller is stale"
+
+      - alert: MLVertexLocalHandoffErrors
+        expr: increase(ml_vertex_local_handoff_runs_total{status="error"}[30m]) > 0
+        for: 5m
+        labels: { severity: warning }
+        annotations:
+          summary: "vertex local fallback handoff controller has errors"
+
+      - alert: MLVertexLocalHandoffExcessiveLocalRouting
+        expr: increase(ml_vertex_local_handoff_routed_total{route="local"}[30m]) > 20
+        for: 10m
+        labels: { severity: warning }
+        annotations:
+          summary: "vertex local handoff is routing many requests to local fallback"
diff --git a/orderflow_services/runbook_ml_phase3_1_vertex_local_handoff_v1.md b/orderflow_services/runbook_ml_phase3_1_vertex_local_handoff_v1.md
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..5555555
--- /dev/null
+++ b/orderflow_services/runbook_ml_phase3_1_vertex_local_handoff_v1.md
@@ -0,0 +1,60 @@
+# Phase 3.1 — Vertex → Local Fallback Handoff Controller
+
+## Цель
+Добавить bounded handoff между Vertex-based contour и local fallback plane.
+
+## Что делает
+- принимает requests в `stream:ml:vertex_local_handoff_requests`
+- при нормальном состоянии Vertex шлёт в primary Vertex stream
+- при деградации Vertex или `force_local=1` шлёт в `stream:ml:local_fallback_requests`
+- для RCA-family не подменяет Vertex полноценным локальным RCA, а создаёт только bounded fallback task:
+  - `vertex_unavailable_fallback`
+
+## Supported task_family
+- `routing_incident_rca`
+- `route_incident_rca`
+- `local_report`
+- `offline_debug`
+- `emergency_summarize`
+
+## Streams
+- input: `stream:ml:vertex_local_handoff_requests`
+- local out: `stream:ml:local_fallback_requests`
+- decisions: `stream:ml:vertex_local_handoff_decisions`
+- audit: `stream:ml:vertex_local_handoff_audit`
+
+## Safe start
+```bash
+export ML_VERTEX_LOCAL_HANDOFF_MODE=AUTO
+export ML_VERTEX_LOCAL_HANDOFF_REQUIRE_VERTEX_DEGRADED=1
+export ML_VERTEX_LOCAL_HANDOFF_VERTEX_HEALTH_HASH=metrics:ml:vertex_health:last
+```
+
+## Smoke checks
+```bash
+redis-cli XADD stream:ml:vertex_local_handoff_requests * \
+  request_id vh-1 \
+  task_family route_incident_rca \
+  incident_id route-inc-1 \
+  severity critical \
+  vertex_unavailable 1 \
+  payload_json '{"summary":"vertex unavailable","primary_reason_codes":["VERTEX_DOWN"]}' \
+  ts_ms $(date +%s%3N)
+
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:vertex_local_handoff_decisions + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:local_fallback_requests + - COUNT 3
+redis-cli XREVRANGE stream:ml:vertex_local_handoff_audit + - COUNT 5
+curl -s localhost:9917/metrics | grep '^ml_vertex_local_handoff_'
+```
